Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.94,0:00:05.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From a different point of view, even an enormous\Nwall obstructing you can become a large door.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.04,0:00:08.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An unexpected twist at\Na movie's preview screening!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.09,0:00:09.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A false start to a case thanks to the Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.72,0:00:11.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.24,0:00:12.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.78,0:00:14.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:17.07,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The game is over - You have no way out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:20.03,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You are out, Dark Sasim!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:21.62,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What are you saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.78,0:02:24.49,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Can you catch a bigshot...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:27.20,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}...like me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.46,0:02:39.34,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't think...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:44.22,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Feel, like water...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.14,0:02:52.06,Signs,,0,0,0,,Simultaneous worldwide release on October 30th!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:02:58.36,Signs,,0,0,0,,Witness the conclusion of the legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:02:58.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Witness this event of the century!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.03,0:03:07.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yet another huge line...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:08.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:12.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the conclusion of a popular movie series that's been going for 20 years, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.08,0:03:18.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we were lucky to get tickets to a preview screening of a movie like that, weren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:20.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You got them from Yoko Okino{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:23.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Be thankful!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:27.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who got the old man to ask her, since I had nothing to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:30.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:36.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, feel the power of Dark Sasim, master swordsman of the dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.65,0:03:40.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The master fencer of light, Bey Jū, won't allow such power!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:45.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll finish you off with the sun-sword of Kisasa, the female warrior of fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.25,0:03:53.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}They're not exactly thanking me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.09,0:04:04.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on! Line up properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:06.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what? We have tickets, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.89,0:04:10.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can just get in when the time comes without having to get in line.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:13.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the seats are first-come-first-serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:15.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't line up you won't get good seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:20.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even so, when we think about how we're going to watch the movie before our friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.61,0:04:22.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We get excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:24.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't sit still!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:27.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you've gotta get into the parts well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:30.45,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Bungo Tatei
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:30.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dark Sasim's two-sword style is wielded
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:35.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,with the large sword in the right hand, and the short sword in the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:39.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, Bey Jū's eyepatch is on the left eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:41.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Kisasa's sun-sword is long, so
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:43.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you have to stretch it like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:46.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So cool! It extends!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:48.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're quite knowledgable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:49.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:52.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, I have the same goods as them...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:54.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hmph, a fanboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:57.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you like Star Blade too, mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:05:02.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You bet... Ever since I watched the first part when I was your age, I've been a big fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:07.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, I met my girlfriend at a preview screening of this series.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:10.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did she not come today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:13.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no... Some things happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:14.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you two have a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:18.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you only get one ticket?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.71,0:05:20.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's not like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:24.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though my friend Narukawa, who's also a fan of Star Blade,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:29.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,kept calling me last night trying to convince me to give him this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:30.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:33.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be careful holding it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:35.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a very important ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:37.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.64,0:05:39.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not long until the opening now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:42.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, it's Dark Takio, the dark swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:44.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:45.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:47.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then how about I take a photo of you with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.11,0:05:48.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:51.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, now give me a big smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:05:55.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:56.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:05:58.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:06:01.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not at all, in fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:02.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,this is what I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:04.55,Signs,,0,0,0,,Bungo Tatei\NFreelance photographer
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:04.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bungo Tatei{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:07.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A photographer, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:08.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:11.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I can assure you they'll come out good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:14.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In return, want us to take a photo of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.43,0:06:15.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:18.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I'll do it with that camera...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:20.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:22.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:24.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then so I can send you the photo,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:26.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,write your name and address in this notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:28.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, yeah, sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:30.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:35.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you write it down?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:36.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:40.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll send it to you once it's been developed and printed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:43.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To this address, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.71,0:06:47.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's free, of course, so don't worry about it.{Of course, I'm not asking for payment, so don't worry.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:51.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to watch Dark Takio!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:54.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! How will this movie end?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:56.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's so strong that I get excited when I see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:57.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:07:02.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Bey Jū and Kisasa will take care of Dark Takio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:04.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Evil never triumphs, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:06.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:10.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh. Somebody's calling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:12.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello? Tatei here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:14.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, Narukawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:15.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.91,0:07:18.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to the Okuho II Building straight away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.70,0:07:21.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Okay... Right. I'll go right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:26.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I apologize, but would you mind holding my place in the line?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:28.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll leave my things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:29.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.59,0:07:30.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:33.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:37.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd that guy ask you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:38.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:40.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn't take your money or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.85,0:07:43.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, he just took a picture of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.31,0:07:47.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before, he kept insisting on taking one of us, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:49.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:51.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We thought he must've been some new type of swindler...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:54.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess we were wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:02.12,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Jōji Narukawa
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:01.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Narukawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:02.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:05.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez. What was that call before about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:08.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the one who told me to call when I got here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:11.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, it was a little misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.42,0:08:13.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's nothing important, I'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:16.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't have enough free time to waste it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.01,0:08:19.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Relax, I'm sure you'll like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:22.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a present...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:26.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...that I've put my heart into, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.81,0:08:30.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy from before really said something odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:31.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:35.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saying that Kisasa and Bey Jū would take out Dark Takio...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:38.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said something like "evil will fall".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:42.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm? Isn't it usual for evil to be punished by allies of justice?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:46.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Dark Takio turned good in the last movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:49.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He rebelled against Dark Sasim!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:54.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When he took off his skull mask, he was really handsome, so he {\i1}has{\i0} to be a good guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:56.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So why did he say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.64,0:08:59.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he'll betray them in this movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:00.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:05.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He probably didn't watch Star Blade V.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:08.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't search through other people's stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:12.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, two tickets for the preview screening from three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:15.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were wedged in his notebook, unused.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:20.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that stain on one of the tickets?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.08,0:09:21.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Probably blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:23.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though it looks like it's been there a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:25.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:29.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What if... What if he had a bloody fight to get them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.59,0:09:32.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:34.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the owners of the tickets...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:39.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...were that Tatei guy, and the woman in this photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:41.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:45.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a photo taken inside a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:48.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The date on it is the same as the one on the tickets from three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:52.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why didn't they go to the preview screening?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.23,0:09:53.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.48,0:09:56.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The lift?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:10:01.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's at the end of the hallway, on the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:03.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:07.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Narukawa! The lift's on the left side of the hallway!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:08.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:11.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We would've found it easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.50,0:10:14.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm terrible with directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.55,0:10:17.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:19.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's odd?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:21.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're just notes, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:27.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Earlier, Tatei tore out the page where the Doc wrote his address on,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:30.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and put it in the case with the film, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:36.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought he did it to make sure he didn't forget what's on the film, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:38.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...all the films are numbered,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:43.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and it seems he details in this notebook what's on each film.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:47.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no remnants of other pages having been torn out of the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:50.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And all the finished films are inside this bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.67,0:10:54.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So why just that film?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.22,0:11:02.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, show it to me already! What's this present you were talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:06.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be so impatient. I'll give it to you in a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:09.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In just the right place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:13.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Talking about the film, I remember something odd about it too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:18.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After I took his photo, he rewound it straight away,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:21.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,even though there was still enough film for 15 photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:23.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that odd?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:26.95,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A film taken out half-way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:31.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Deliberately tearing out the Doc's address and putting it in his pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:34.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And a pair of tickets for the preview screening from three years ago, tainted with blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:38.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A friend, also a fan of Star Blade, who called him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:43.39,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It can't be! He...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:45.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tatei...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:49.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it okay to be here? This is the roof...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:50.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you remember, Narukawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:51.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.18,0:11:53.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was sunny, like today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:55.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the day of that preview screening,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:12:00.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when we met Ami.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:02.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got it! I understand it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.86,0:12:06.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He must've come to the preview screening as part of his job!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:10.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he took out the film to keep his professional photos separate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:11.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:16.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he was here on a job, he wouldn't have been lining up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:18.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:21.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.13,0:12:26.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he no longer intends to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.19,0:12:36.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.61,0:12:40.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't tell me you forgot. It was only six years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.98,0:12:46.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course I remember. We met Ami at the preview screening for Star Blade IV.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.87,0:12:54.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found her lost nearby, clenching her ticket, and escorted her to the cinema.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.66,0:12:58.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Six years ago, it was the same cinema as today...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:13:02.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the same cinema as three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:04.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait. Are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:08.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you {\i1}still{\i0} angry about the accident that killed Ami three years ago?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.22,0:13:11.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,True, I {\i1}was{\i0} the one driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:16.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But even the police said the truck driver was at fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:20.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He fell asleep and wasn't obeying the traffic lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:24.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:28.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure, I {\i1}did{\i0} oversleep that day and was in a hurry,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:31.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I wasn't going too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:37.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you bringing up that again {\i1}now{\i0}, and in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:41.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here. It's the present I promised you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:46.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whoa! A ticket to the Star Blade preview screening!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:50.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You called me asking if I had any spare, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.97,0:13:53.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you said you didn't last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.64,0:13:56.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I got a job at the last minute so I can't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:13:59.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I called you this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:04.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Plus, I figured Ami'd be happy if I gave it to you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.82,0:14:09.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, the accident happened right near the base of this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:12.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:16.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ever since the accident, things've been tense between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:18.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So take it, as proof of our reconciliation!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:25.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, also, there's only five minutes until the opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.63,0:14:29.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't hurry, you won't make it to the pre-screening event!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:30.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.64,0:14:32.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, thank you, Tatei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.55,0:14:35.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're welcome! Make sure you watch it instead of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:36.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You betcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:41.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll burn the role of your favorite character, Dark Takio, into my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.52,0:14:45.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though whatever happens, I'm sure Bey Jū and Kisasa will finish him off in the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.19,0:14:46.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:48.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next time we meet, I'll treat you to something for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:50.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:00.96,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ami...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:07.67,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sorry for leaving you alone for three years...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.22,0:15:16.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.18,0:15:20.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Now I too... can be with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:24.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's useless...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:31.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if you jump now, it'll just be seen as suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:36.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because I'll testify...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.99,0:15:40.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That I saw you climb over the fence by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.87,0:15:42.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:45.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're one of the kids who were in the line, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:47.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think you're misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:50.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just climbed up to take a look at the scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.22,0:15:52.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The plot you wrote went like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:58.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, you planned to pick a suitable group from the line
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:02.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and make friends with them, saying you were a big Star Blade fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.10,0:16:04.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take a picture of them with your camera...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.48,0:16:11.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have them write their name and address in your notebook, saying you'd send them their picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:15.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tear out that page, and place it in your pocket with the film.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:21.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd previously called a friend out,\Ntelling him "Call me when you get there".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.41,0:16:28.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And once he did, you'd say his name and the place out loud, so those friends would remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.50,0:16:33.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, you'd leave the line,\Ntelling them you'd be back soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.51,0:16:36.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd meet with your friend, make him come up to this roof,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:38.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then after handing him the ticket you would just have to jump off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:44.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, the ones you picked for the role of your friends were us...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:48.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So when our address and photo were discovered on your corpse,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:51.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,of course the police would contact us...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:57.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And hearing us testify that you were surely a movie fan,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.62,0:17:02.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and your friend who called you wanted your ticket...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:09.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once they confirmed that your friend attended the preview screening with a ticket with your fingerprints on...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:11.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The police would conclude...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:22.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That your friend called you here right before the preview screening, pushed you off the roof of this building, and stole your ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:27.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Incidentally, you deliberately asked where the lift was
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.94,0:17:30.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to make sure that they'd remember you were with a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:36.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you deliberately dropped the ticket so my friend's fingerprints would get on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:41.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the preview screening,\Nwhen the police recover the tickets,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.53,0:17:46.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,if a ticket shows up with your, your friend's, and my friend's fingerprints on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.33,0:17:53.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it'll prove that you had the ticket today when you met us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.47,0:17:58.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're smart, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:18:04.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But will the police really believe the testimony and deductions of a single boy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:06.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.39,0:18:09.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if they don't believe one of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.60,0:18:11.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,there's five of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:12.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll make them believe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:17.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, we passed by someone who looks like they might be a friend of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:21.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By now, he'll have left the building and be on his way to the cinema.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.45,0:18:28.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if you were to jump now, time-wise it'd be impossible, so your trick won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.29,0:18:30.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{By the way, we ran into that so-called friend of yours with the ticket just now. <- Deleted -uso.} Too bad for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.33,0:18:31.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.29,0:18:34.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't understand how I feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:35.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:42.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three years ago, he was driving the car your girlfriend was in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:45.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was an accident, and she died. That's your motive, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.35,0:18:47.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you know that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:51.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your notebook had tickets and a photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:56.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The tickets were for the preview screening of Star Blade V, from three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.15,0:19:01.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The photo shows you and a girl as a couple, riding in a car's back seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:06.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely, the photo was taken by the driver, a friend who'd push the shutter for you.{seems to be some sort of JP phrase}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.49,0:19:10.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, there was blood on one of the tickets
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:14.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the photo had the same date as the preview screening, so I got a general idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:19.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That day, you couldn't attend the preview screening because of an accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:28.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and it's likely that the cause was the driver,\Nthe friend you tried to make out to be a killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:31.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:34.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he hadn't overslept that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:38.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If only he'd come at the time we'd arranged...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.19,0:19:42.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'd never have crossed paths with that damn truck...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.70,0:19:50.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that resentment's unjustified.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:55.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know! I've been telling myself that over and over again to restrain my heart!{STOP}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:59.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then he called me for the first time in 3 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:03.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just to ask me if I happened to have an extra ticket to Star Blade VI!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.59,0:20:10.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then he happily took that ticket and headed off to the cinema...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.43,0:20:13.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As if he forgot what happened three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.39,0:20:17.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His mind full of Dark Takio and Bey Jū's confrontation...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.19,0:20:19.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those two aren't gonna fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.98,0:20:23.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dark Takio's on Bey Jū's side now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.61,0:20:25.07,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.07,0:20:28.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Neither he nor his friend got to watch Star Blade V...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.29,0:20:32.75,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Then, if he wanted the ticket, that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.75,0:20:36.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, was the accident three years ago close by?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:39.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah... That's why I was gonna jump from this building...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:40.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take me there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:47.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:50.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the guy we passed by leaving the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.35,0:20:53.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's not the way to the cinema...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.06,0:20:54.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Narukawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.85,0:20:56.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well? Where was the accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.60,0:20:57.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:21:03.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The truck hit us and threw us against this guard rail.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:07.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? There's something there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:10.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.74,0:21:12.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:15.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ticket to the preview screening of Star Blade VI!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.04,0:21:20.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's another ticket here, from three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.21,0:21:23.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This one's weathered from wind and rain though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.05,0:21:25.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But... why did he...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.13,0:21:27.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:29.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wanted that woman to see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.51,0:21:33.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By leaving them as an offering where she died, they might make it to heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.93,0:21:39.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, the fact that he didn't mention it to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.86,0:21:42.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...indicates he was probably in love with her too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.07,0:21:47.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He loved your girlfriend... just as much as you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.37,0:23:21.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't mind myself, but the event before the screening ends in three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.25,0:23:25.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, come with us to the preview screening!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.75,0:23:29.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can watch the movie and tell Ami about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.13,0:23:32.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We happen to have a spare ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.01,0:23:35.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Since the old man passed on watching it...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.22,0:23:37.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.97,0:23:39.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'll leave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.52,0:23:41.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't watched V yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.60,0:23:42.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And well...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.15,0:23:47.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll buy Star Blade V and VI's DVDs,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.40,0:23:49.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and watch them at his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.45,0:23:58.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.05,0:24:12.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The mini-cars, figures and books lined up on the shelves...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.63,0:24:17.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...they're almost all upside down.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.18,0:24:19.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.90,0:24:29.94,Signs,,0,0,0,,The Upside-Down Conclusion
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.90,0:24:29.94,Signs,,0,0,0,,(Part I)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.90,0:24:28.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the next Conan: The Upside-Down Conclusion (Part I)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.94,0:24:34.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Collection!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.91,0:24:36.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next time, a strange collector shows up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.70,0:24:38.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Haibara, what do you collect?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.45,0:24:42.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a secret.
